{
    "name": "Facebook不要再給我大字了！",
    "description": "有些人簡短的貼文Facebook會把它變成大字，看得很不習慣嗎？裝這款外掛讓字體大小變正常吧！",
    "version": "0.0.1",
    "manifest_version": 2,
    "content_scripts": [{
        "matches": ["*://*.facebook.com/*"],
        "css": ["normal_font.css"]
    }],
    "browser_action": {
        "default_icon": "icon/icon32.png",
        "default_popup": "popup.html"
    },
    "icons": {
        "16": "icon/icon16.png",
        "32": "icon/icon32.png",
        "64": "icon/icon64.png",
        "128": "icon/icon128.png"
    }
}